    10→ * will only include 0 and/or 1.
    11→ */
    12→public class PyBoolNode extends APyNode<PyBoolObj> {
    13→
    14→    /**
    15→     * Generates all valid PyBoolObjs within the exhaustive domain. Interprets 0 (in
    16→     * the exhaustive domain) as False and 1 as True.
    17→     *
    18→     * @return a set of PyBoolObjs comprising the exhaustive domain
    19→     */
